      <a href="#signup" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-brand-600 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow hover:bg-brand-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-600/50">Sign Up Online</a>
